    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready to go? This car is a solid choice for anyone seeking a functional and reliable vehicle! While it shows some honest signs of use and visible wear both inside and out, it has been well-loved and is still a great performer on the road. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a reliable car at a budget-friendly price point!",
