      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the absolute highest standard available on the pre-owned market. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original deep factory luster with no scratches, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin is in pristine state; the upholstery shows zero signs of wear, and every interior feature, from the infotainment system to the climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. It drives exactly as it did when new, offering a smooth, quiet, and powerful experience with no mechanical issues or leaks of any kind. A buyer can expect a turn-key vehicle that is indistinguishable from a new car, suitable for a collector or a buyer who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
