      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning motorist. Demonstrating consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic, it offers a sophisticated synthesis of performance and enduring value. All primary systems have been rigorously evaluated to ensure continued reliability and roadworthiness, presenting a standard of quality that exceeds typical market expectations.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
