      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and it\u2019s still in wonderful shape, running smooth as butter. It's been well-loved and is super clean inside and out. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know it'll make its next owner very happy! Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S represents a pinnacle of mid-engine balance. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.4L flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and VarioCam Plus, the powerplant delivers linear torque through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, benefitting from a low polar moment of inertia and precise electromechanical steering. Maintenance is up to date",
      "price": 35000.0,
