      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Reliable daily driver. Engine runs strong. Clean interior. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Maintenance records up to date.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear expected of a well-loved car, such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple with minimal wear on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive inspection. It shifts smoothly, brakes firmly, and sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires. Complete with a full service history and two sets of keys, this car is ready for its next owner to enjoy a reliable and premium driving experience.",
      "price": 34850.0,
